      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You ever see a car and just know it\u2019s been someone\u2019s absolute pride and joy? That\u2019s this beauty right here. Honestly, it\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed on Sundays, and it still has that 'new car' feeling when you slide into the seat. It drives so smooth you\u2019ll forget you\u2019re even on the road. There might be a tiny, tiny blemish if you look with a magnifying glass, but to me, she\u2019s practically perfect. I\u2019m only letting her go to a home that\u2019ll love her as much as I do. Come by for a coffee and a test drive, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 48500.0,
